transcript:
Executive: Haan ji sir. Haan haan 15-20 minute mein sir join karna aap.
Customer: Theek hai?
Executive: Sir jaldi kara do ji. Haan 15 minute ka 9 baje ka time tha 9 baje se aapko 9:15 baje phone maar diya tha ji.
Customer: Achcha aaya tha mere paas call to dikha nahi kuch.
Executive: Haan aapne uthaya nahi ji dekho.
Customer: Theek hai, theek hai.
Executive: Wo aise hai na fir beech mein bachche ne usko jana hai ji isliye tha.
Customer: Chalo karwao koi baat nahi hai ji. Karwa do.
Executive: Theek hai ji, theek hai.
